ğŸ’¡ Want to Capture More?
Change the filter for other ports:

python
Copy
Edit
PORT_FILTER = "tcp port 80"           # HTTP only
PORT_FILTER = "tcp port 80 or 443"    # HTTP & HTTPS
PORT_FILTER = "ip"                    # All IP traffic
